\/salat-on-time-delayed-jamaah\/","url_meta":{"origin":8044,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Pray on time if congregation is delayed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to me, \u201cO Abu Dharr, how will you be if your leaders delay the prayer from its proper time, or let it die altogether?\" I said, \u201cWhat do you command me to do?\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26198,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/04\/08\/sun-under-control-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":8044,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sun: The sun is under the control of Allah Almighty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him when the sun had set, \u201cDo you know where it has gone?\u201d Abu Dharr said, \u201cAllah and His Messenger know best.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, it has gone until it prostrates under the Throne. It seeks\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8044","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyha